				<div class="postentry">
					<p>This was from my wife she also took all the pictures</p>
<p>Hi,</p>
<p>We were blessed with plentiful rain in the summer and we are blessed<br />
with plentiful snow this winter.  What a difference a season makes!<br />
Hope you enjoy seeing the difference.</p>
<p>The 10 inches today was beautiful and very fluffy, it was also much<br />
warmer today, up in the 20&#8242;s.</p>
<p>Have a wonderful Holiday Season.</p>
<p>Donna</p>
